  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/4105f31f4a2c01784349a864a22d4dfa.poster.avif?t=1729951009\" width=800 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/4105f31f4a2c01784349a864a22d4dfa.webm?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/4105f31f4a2c01784349a864a22d4dfa.mp4?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warmage</strong> is a <strong>roguelite grid-based turn-based tactical combat</strong> game where you play as a young warmage tasked with defending his city against an unknown evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as 12 different archetypes with unique gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied and refreshing tactical combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each battle, power up your warmage and buy various attacks and items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your next mission on the city map carefully</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Differents objectives for each battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 96 spells and 55 items to combine to create the ultimate warmage</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/799fad57e9dab3be2259106c0024c237.poster.avif?t=1729951009\" width=724 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/799fad57e9dab3be2259106c0024c237.webm?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/799fad57e9dab3be2259106c0024c237.mp4?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a wide variety of weapons and spells to defeat waves of enemies in a turn by turn combat. Various enemies will challenge you in different ways, think carefully about each movement and each attack as a single error can put you in perilous situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/1ccfe2ee713674c2ee2ab2f88bd28e6c.poster.avif?t=1729951009\" width=724 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/1ccfe2ee713674c2ee2ab2f88bd28e6c.webm?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/1ccfe2ee713674c2ee2ab2f88bd28e6c.mp4?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the gems collected during the fights to buy new spells, upgrade the ones you already have and buy new items. With each level gained, you can upgrade one of your primary characteristics which will improve the power of your attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/ffcca01ad1f887b5a3227591b8e92a2e.avif?t=1729951009\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras_big/ffcca01ad1f887b5a3227591b8e92a2e.avif?t=1729951009 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Burn them all</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now that you have a deadly warmage with powerfull spells, defeat all whom will stand in your way !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/b058cc043947ddf037c5f341c0190e70.poster.avif?t=1729951009\" width=436 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/b058cc043947ddf037c5f341c0190e70.webm?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/b058cc043947ddf037c5f341c0190e70.mp4?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Use your environment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The surroundings aren't just for show, they can be your greatest ally in escaping deadly situations. Learn to harness them to your advantage !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/e8f187bd4ade0b901890d8133b0d53cf.poster.avif?t=1729951009\" width=800 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/e8f187bd4ade0b901890d8133b0d53cf.webm?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/e8f187bd4ade0b901890d8133b0d53cf.mp4?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Defend your city</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your city is attacked by an unknown evil. You have to help the citizens, others warmages and important people to survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/f755f6067c7ca460968519f18b6e2584.avif?t=1729951009\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras_big/f755f6067c7ca460968519f18b6e2584.avif?t=1729951009 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/4105f31f4a2c01784349a864a22d4dfa.poster.avif?t=1729951009\" width=800 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/4105f31f4a2c01784349a864a22d4dfa.webm?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/4105f31f4a2c01784349a864a22d4dfa.mp4?t=1729951009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Warmage</strong> is a <strong>roguelite grid-based turn-based tactical combat</strong> game where you play as a young warmage tasked with defending his city against an unknown evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as 12 different archetypes with unique gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied and refreshing tactical combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each battle, power up your warmage and buy various attacks and items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your next mission on the city map carefully</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Differents objectives for each battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 96 spells and 55 items to combine to create the ultimate warmage</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/799fad57e9dab3be2259106c0024c237.poster.avif?t=1729951009\" width=724 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/799fad57e9dab3be2259106c0024c237.webm?t=1729951009\" type=\"v