citizens, others warmages and important people to survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras/f755f6067c7ca460968519f18b6e2584.avif?t=1729951009\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648980/extras_big/f755f6067c7ca460968519f18b6e2584.avif?t=1729951009 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
